测试的用的bugselect a.id as aid, a.name as aName from tbAccount a, tbBank b where a.tbBank_id = b.id and bankId = 'a004'  and a.tbaccountType_id = 2
getUniqueSubAccount=select id as sid from tbsubAccount where tbaccount_id =2 and tbCurrency_id = 1
userbillSQL=SELECT e.id AS eid, a.id AS aid, transdate, tbPayee_id, tbCategory2_id, type, c.name as cname, amount, direction, tbSubAccount_id, tbSubAccount_id1, a.tbPayee_id AS pid,direction AS deric, a.comment AS acomment, type, e.name AS dname, d.name AS aname, b.name AS bname, f.name AS fname, c.name AS cname, g.name as payeeName FROM tbTransaction a, tbCategory2 b, tbCategory1 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e, tbCurrency f LEFT JOIN tbPayee g ON a.tbpayee_id=g.id  WHERE b.tbCategory1_id=c.id AND a.tbCategory2_id=b.id AND a.tbSubAccount_id=e.id AND e.tbAccount_id=d.id AND f.id=e.tbCurrency_id  and d.id = 2 and transactionClasses = 0 
 select count(a.id) as myNum from tbtransaction a, tbcategory1 b, tbcategory2 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e  where e.tbAccount_id = d.id and a.tbsubaccount_id = e.id and a.tbcategory2_id = c.id and c.tbcategory1_id = b.id  and sign = '20110806' and transactionClasses = 1 and e.tbCurrency_id = 1 and d.keyinfo = '3912'  and b.type = 0 and amount =146.40:::::
sql执行完毕=select a.id as aid from tbtransaction a, tbcategory1 b, tbcategory2 c, tbsubaccount d, tbaccount e, tbbank f  where a.tbsubaccount_id = d.id and d.tbAccount_id = e.id and a.tbcategory2_id = c.id and c.tbcategory1_id = b.id and transactionClasses = 1 and f.id  = e.tbBank_id and  transdate in ( '2011-08-06',date('2011-08-06','-1 day') ) and f.bankid = 'e001'  and e.tbAccountType_id = 4 and direction = '' and b.type = 0 and amount =146.40 and a.id not in () order by transdate asc limit 1
 select count(a.id) as myNum from tbtransaction a, tbcategory1 b, tbcategory2 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e  where e.tbAccount_id = d.id and a.tbsubaccount_id = e.id and a.tbcategory2_id = c.id and c.tbcategory1_id = b.id  and sign = '20110806' and transactionClasses = 1 and e.tbCurrency_id = 1 and d.keyinfo = '3912'  and b.type = 0 and amount =77.80:::::

userbillSQL=SELECT e.id AS eid, a.id AS aid, transdate, tbPayee_id, tbCategory2_id, type, c.name as cname, amount, direction, tbSubAccount_id, tbSubAccount_id1, a.tbPayee_id AS pid,direction AS deric, a.comment AS acomment, type, e.name AS dname, d.name AS aname, b.name AS bname, f.name AS fname, c.name AS cname, g.name as payeeName FROM tbTransaction a, tbCategory2 b, tbCategory1 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e, tbCurrency f LEFT JOIN tbPayee g ON a.tbpayee_id=g.id  WHERE b.tbCategory1_id=c.id AND a.tbCategory2_id=b.id AND a.tbSubAccount_id=e.id AND e.tbAccount_id=d.id AND f.id=e.tbCurrency_id  and d.id = 8 and transactionClasses = 0

getUniqueSubAccount=select id as sid from tbsubAccount where tbaccount_id =13 and tbCurrency_id = 1
getUniqueSubAccount=select id as sid from tbsubAccount where tbaccount_id =13 and tbCurrency_id = 2
userbillSQL=SELECT e.id AS eid, a.id AS aid, transdate, tbPayee_id, tbCategory2_id, type, c.name as cname, amount, direction, tbSubAccount_id, tbSubAccount_id1, a.tbPayee_id AS pid,direction AS deric, a.comment AS acomment, type, e.name AS dname, d.name AS aname, b.name AS bname, f.name AS fname, c.name AS cname, g.name as payeeName FROM tbTransaction a, tbCategory2 b, tbCategory1 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e, tbCurrency f LEFT JOIN tbPayee g ON a.tbpayee_id=g.id  WHERE b.tbCategory1_id=c.id AND a.tbCategory2_id=b.id AND a.tbSubAccount_id=e.id AND e.tbAccount_id=d.id AND f.id=e.tbCurrency_id  and d.id = 13 and transactionClasses = 0 
 select count(a.id) as myNum from tbtransaction a, tbcategory1 b, tbcategory2 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e  where e.tbAccount_id = d.id and a.tbsubaccount_id = e.id and a.tbcategory2_id = c.id and c.tbcategory1_id = b.id  and sign = '20100930' and transactionClasses = 1 and e.tbCurrency_id = 1 and d.keyinfo = '6897'  and b.type = 1 and amount = abs(-510.00):::::
sql执行完毕=select a.id as aid from tbtransaction a, tbcategory1 b, tbcategory2 c, tbsubaccount d, tbaccount e, tbbank f  where a.tbsubaccount_id = d.id and d.tbAccount_id = e.id and a.tbcategory2_id = c.id and c.tbcategory1_id = b.id and transactionClasses = 1 and f.id  = e.tbBank_id and  transdate in ( '2010-09-30',date('2010-09-30','-1 day') ) and f.bankid = 'e001'  and e.tbAccountType_id = 4 and direction = '' and b.type = 1 and amount = abs(-510.00) and a.id not in () order by transdate asc limit 1

getUniqueSubAccount=select id as sid from tbsubAccount where tbaccount_id =12 and tbCurrency_id = 1
userbillSQL=SELECT e.id AS eid, a.id AS aid, transdate, tbPayee_id, tbCategory2_id, type, c.name as cname, amount, direction, tbSubAccount_id, tbSubAccount_id1, a.tbPayee_id AS pid,direction AS deric, a.comment AS acomment, type, e.name AS dname, d.name AS aname, b.name AS bname, f.name AS fname, c.name AS cname, g.name as payeeName FROM tbTransaction a, tbCategory2 b, tbCategory1 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e, tbCurrency f LEFT JOIN tbPayee g ON a.tbpayee_id=g.id  WHERE b.tbCategory1_id=c.id AND a.tbCategory2_id=b.id AND a.tbSubAccount_id=e.id AND e.tbAccount_id=d.id AND f.id=e.tbCurrency_id  and d.id = 12 and transactionClasses = 0 
 select count(a.id) as myNum from tbtransaction a, tbcategory1 b, tbcategory2 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e  where e.tbAccount_id = d.id and a.tbsubaccount_id = e.id and a.tbcategory2_id = c.id and c.tbcategory1_id = b.id  and sign = '20110806' and transactionClasses = 1 and e.tbCurrency_id = 1 and d.keyinfo = '3912'  and b.type = 0 and amount =146.40:::::
sql执行完毕=select a.id as aid from tbtransaction a, tbcategory1 b, tbcategory2 c, tbsubaccount d, tbaccount e, tbbank f  where a.tbsubaccount_id = d.id and d.tbAccount_id = e.id and a.tbcategory2_id = c.id and c.tbcategory1_id = b.id and transactionClasses = 1 and f.id  = e.tbBank_id and  transdate in ( '2011-08-06',date('2011-08-06','-1 day') ) and f.bankid = 'e001'  and e.tbAccountType_id = 4 and direction = '' and b.type = 0 and amount =146.40 and a.id not in () order by transdate asc limit 1
 select count(a.id) as myNum from tbtransaction a, tbcategory1 b, tbcategory2 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e  where e.tbAccount_id = d.id and a.tbsubaccount_id = e.id and a.tbcategory2_id = c.id and c.tbcategory1_id = b.id  and sign = '20110806' and transactionClasses = 1 and e.tbCurrency_id = 1 and d.keyinfo = '3912'  and b.type = 0 and amount =77.80:::::

userbillSQL=SELECT e.id AS eid, a.id AS aid, transdate, tbPayee_id, tbCategory2_id, type, c.name as cname, amount, direction, tbSubAccount_id, tbSubAccount_id1, a.tbPayee_id AS pid,direction AS deric, a.comment AS acomment, type, e.name AS dname, d.name AS aname, b.name AS bname, f.name AS fname, c.name AS cname, g.name as payeeName FROM tbTransaction a, tbCategory2 b, tbCategory1 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e, tbCurrency f LEFT JOIN tbPayee g ON a.tbpayee_id=g.id  WHERE b.tbCategory1_id=c.id AND a.tbCategory2_id=b.id AND a.tbSubAccount_id=e.id AND e.tbAccount_id=d.id AND f.id=e.tbCurrency_id  and d.id = 13 and transactionClasses = 0

userbillSQL=SELECT e.id AS eid, a.id AS aid, transdate, tbPayee_id, tbCategory2_id, type, c.name as cname, amount, direction, tbSubAccount_id, tbSubAccount_id1, a.tbPayee_id AS pid,direction AS deric, a.comment AS acomment, type, e.name AS dname, d.name AS aname, b.name AS bname, f.name AS fname, c.name AS cname, g.name as payeeName FROM tbTransaction a, tbCategory2 b, tbCategory1 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e, tbCurrency f LEFT JOIN tbPayee g ON a.tbpayee_id=g.id  WHERE b.tbCategory1_id=c.id AND a.tbCategory2_id=b.id AND a.tbSubAccount_id=e.id AND e.tbAccount_id=d.id AND f.id=e.tbCurrency_id  and d.id = 13 and transactionClasses = 0

getUniqueSubAccount=select id as sid from tbsubAccount where tbaccount_id =12 and tbCurrency_id = 1

userbillSQL=SELECT e.id AS eid, a.id AS aid, transdate, tbPayee_id, tbCategory2_id, type, c.name as cname, amount, direction, tbSubAccount_id, tbSubAccount_id1, a.tbPayee_id AS pid,direction AS deric, a.comment AS acomment, type, e.name AS dname, d.name AS aname, b.name AS bname, f.name AS fname, c.name AS cname, g.name as payeeName FROM tbTransaction a, tbCategory2 b, tbCategory1 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e, tbCurrency f LEFT JOIN tbPayee g ON a.tbpayee_id=g.id  WHERE b.tbCategory1_id=c.id AND a.tbCategory2_id=b.id AND a.tbSubAccount_id=e.id AND e.tbAccount_id=d.id AND f.id=e.tbCurrency_id  and d.id = 12 and transactionClasses = 0

userbillSQL=SELECT e.id AS eid, a.id AS aid, transdate, tbPayee_id, tbCategory2_id, type, c.name as cname, amount, direction, tbSubAccount_id, tbSubAccount_id1, a.tbPayee_id AS pid,direction AS deric, a.comment AS acomment, type, e.name AS dname, d.name AS aname, b.name AS bname, f.name AS fname, c.name AS cname, g.name as payeeName FROM tbTransaction a, tbCategory2 b, tbCategory1 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e, tbCurrency f LEFT JOIN tbPayee g ON a.tbpayee_id=g.id  WHERE b.tbCategory1_id=c.id AND a.tbCategory2_id=b.id AND a.tbSubAccount_id=e.id AND e.tbAccount_id=d.id AND f.id=e.tbCurrency_id  and d.id = 13 and transactionClasses = 0

getUniqueSubAccount=select id as sid from tbsubAccount where tbaccount_id =13 and tbCurrency_id = 1
getUniqueSubAccount=select id as sid from tbsubAccount where tbaccount_id =13 and tbCurrency_id = 2
userbillSQL=SELECT substr(transdate,0,4) as myYear, substr(transdate,6,2) as myMonth, e.id AS eid, a.id AS aid, transdate, tbPayee_id, tbCategory2_id, type, c.name as cname, amount, direction, tbSubAccount_id, tbSubAccount_id1, a.tbPayee_id AS pid,direction AS deric, a.comment AS acomment, type, e.name AS dname, d.name AS aname, b.name AS bname, f.name AS fname, c.name AS cname, g.name as payeeName FROM tbTransaction a, tbCategory2 b, tbCategory1 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e, tbCurrency f LEFT JOIN tbPayee g ON a.tbpayee_id=g.id  WHERE b.tbCategory1_id=c.id AND a.tbCategory2_id=b.id AND a.tbSubAccount_id=e.id AND e.tbAccount_id=d.id AND f.id=e.tbCurrency_id  and d.id = 13 and transactionClasses = 0 
 select count(a.id) as myNum from tbtransaction a, tbcategory1 b, tbcategory2 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e  where e.tbAccount_id = d.id and a.tbsubaccount_id = e.id and a.tbcategory2_id = c.id and c.tbcategory1_id = b.id  and sign = '20110917' and transactionClasses = 1 and e.tbCurrency_id = 1 and d.keyinfo = '6897'  and b.type = 0 and amount =308.60:::::
sql执行完毕=select a.id as aid from tbtransaction a, tbcategory1 b, tbcategory2 c, tbsubaccount d, tbaccount e, tbbank f  where a.tbsubaccount_id = d.id and d.tbAccount_id = e.id and a.tbcategory2_id = c.id and c.tbcategory1_id = b.id and transactionClasses = 1 and f.id  = e.tbBank_id and  transdate in ( '2011-09-17',date('2011-09-17','-1 day') ) and f.bankid = 'e001'  and e.tbAccountType_id = 4 and direction = '' and b.type = 0 and amount =308.60 and a.id not in () order by transdate asc limit 1
 select count(a.id) as myNum from tbtransaction a, tbcategory1 b, tbcategory2 c, tbAccount d, tbSubAccount e  where e.tbAccount_id = d.id and a.tbsubaccount_id = e.id and a.tbcategory2_id = c.id and c.tbcategory1_id = b.id  and sign = '20110918' and transactionClasses = 1 and e.tbCurrency_id = 1 and d.keyinfo = '6897'  and b.type = 0 and amount =270.00:::::
sql执行完毕=select a.id as aid from tbtransaction a, tbcategory1 b, tbcategory2 c, tbsubaccount d, tbaccount e, tbbank f  where a.tbsubaccount_id = d.id and d.tbAccount_id = e.id and a.tbcategory2_id = c.id and c.tbcategory1_id = b.id and transactionClasses = 1 and f.id  = e.tbBank_id and  transdate in ( '2011-09-18',date('2011-09-18','-1 day') ) and f.bankid = 'e001'  and e.tbAccountType_id = 4 and direction = '' and b.type = 0 and amount =270.00 and a.id not in () order by transdate asc limit 1
